description:
She may be a sleepy Kansen, but don't be fooled! The Royal Navy and Le Malin are prepped and ready for the Joint Military Exercises!

The Le Malin DLC unlocks the following:

Main Ship (Playable):
• Le Malin

Support Ships:
• Essex
• Baltimore
• Centaur

Story Mode:
• Le Malin - Additional Story Mode content
name: Le Malin Episode
